    "schedule_read": "Bounded group-panel token-tile sidecar HIP/CK valid-dKV rung. The forward group-id sidecar is sorted by compressed group along K and invalid entries are sentinel-coded, so each CTA binary-searches the panel's K subrange instead of rescanning all K512 selected slots. It then keeps the query-major K16 score/prob/scaled-dP producer, accumulates dKV[group,D] in LDS across the token tile, and emits one final global atomic stream for the reduced group panel."
  },
